title: World of Warcraft Private Server Launcher
description:
This is a private server launcher i just got done making for wow.

You can add a server and address, launch the wow client and it will automatically change the realmlist for you, delete a server from your list, and i even added three pics for each of the wow versions ie- regular wow, burning crusade, and lich king, which it will load the last used pic.

send ideas and suggestions or problems to my email

Thanks DeathJS

Version 1.0


Note:It keeps up to 20 servers in the list if you need more let me know! I figured 20 was enough so.

i know there is going to be errors so just send me an email and let me know! I will personalize this program with your logo for $5 usd also

Note: I also included the vb60runtimes for it, sorry i only know vb6 pretty good or else i would use another program that didnt require a dependency.

also if you need a launcher for 3.0.3 let me know as the realmlist.wtf file isnt in the normal place
